{"tid":1561000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"挽回唔到 講到尾 係咪其實已經唔愛了","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T15:46:22.000Z","uid":151451,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae8b1fcea04b52f5e7557f305d5b16d3959855f","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"係咪得我仲傻更更咁以為我地唔會就咁完 以為我地可以一生一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會可以實現承諾結婚 會去好多好多旅行 永遠幸福快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩方法都用盡了 覺得自己成個痴漢咁好變態 覺得係時候要停了<br />\n<br />\n我向自己發咗誓喇 聽日開始唔會再騷擾你 唔會再係樓下等你 唔會再寫信俾你 唔會再叫人幫我搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到尾 係咪其實已經唔愛了 所以挽回唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...<br />\n仲愛嘅話 點解唔可以一齊解決問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好愛你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好唔捨得你 好愛好愛你 愛你仲多過愛我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想睇吓我地未來嘅bb係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係...88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肥妹 你永遠會係我心入面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b0f81d688f6238fc6cc3a569e33a34e88c9d38","tid":1561000,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"【捍衛香港 存亡之秋】915民陣遊行攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560996</a>"},{"pid":"29c3d278f509487b0a07e12b727119822379b44f","tid":1561000,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"db83eba4ccaa2538ff97bca3d792b036d7cc1e06","tid":1561000,"uid":275447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67be23cf2a1d143c40ab9683a789d21f81d9b9c","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db83eba4ccaa2538ff97bca3d792b036d7cc1e06","tid":1561000,"uid":275447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:23.000Z","msg":"無得唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337699502d987fea24d98c1fe48b651a3482b2d7","tid":1561000,"uid":275447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f67be23cf2a1d143c40ab9683a789d21f81d9b9c","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db83eba4ccaa2538ff97bca3d792b036d7cc1e06","tid":1561000,"uid":275447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:23.000Z","msg":"無得唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢唔想都冇辦法，睇下我個名就知啦"},{"pid":"71bf4e0d82ebc6c0a48f4de06d79477f40a51211","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"你知唔知道我真係好愛你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係好愛好愛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我提出嘅野 全部都係為咗我地嘅未來咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔想同我有未來咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔係話係都好愛我㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你都好愛我嘅話 點解唔同我一齊為未來打算啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係為咗呢件事而分手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係plan晒同你嘅未來係點樣㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解你要離開我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好想娶你返屋企啊肥妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4881f7131761e24a16a64a0897a1fa7d40e2072","tid":1561000,"uid":75013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"我都好想嫁比你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你唔肯同返我一齊 點解唔可以一齊渡過呢個冷淡期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c076261f21d908b42945bff0fb0ed7e793f467d","tid":1561000,"uid":31215,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"冇架喇<br />\n向前望<br />\n就好似你飲開凍奶茶，未飲過其他野，以為世界得凍奶茶，忽然間冇得飲梗係失落<br />\n到你遇上凍檸茶，雖然味道唔同，但都好飲，你有時會諗返凍奶茶嘅味，但凍檸茶都夠你快樂"},{"pid":"822da30bee55faa5e2134462e379ea876857d05a","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"為咗令你開心 我付出咗好多㗎喇你知唔知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗陪你去地方 好多時就算攰到死都唔出聲<br />\n為咗買啲野俾你 我特登食少幾餐 要食都食最平<br />\n為咗你開心 就算幾緊張幾尷尬都好 都上你度食飯<br />\n為咗唔好令你孤獨 我由細到大都驚到仆街嘅機動遊戲我都坐上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個海盜船我真係超超超級驚㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上到去玩個陣 飯腳仲狂震 標晒冷汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令你食得開心啲 我每晚都上youtube睇煮野食channels 日日睇吓點樣整牛排會好食啲 想你讚我煮得好食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗你唔孤單 之前每晚我好眼瞓都唔想瞓 就算我知道咁樣做之後會失眠 但我都要陪你傾到天光先瞓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我成日係啲fds面前都忍唔住講我有幾愛你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好努力㗎你知唔知啊 點解 點解要咁絕 連搵都唔俾我搵你啊<br />\n<br />\n我真係好愛你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ee87f1e4940fa1fbc69c6b736b43524fd82c45","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"我淨係想我地未來會輕鬆啲咋 <br />\n我為我地未來嘅家著想咋 <br />\n點解 點解你唔明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d8e3871a99c2822e284a528a491af1340cddd4","tid":1561000,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a7d5bf12fc8fa7f2427faa490324a3bcde16ebb","tid":1561000,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a086d02507a8b25cef4c000590a63eb985ff05","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"我知你都付出咗好多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係點解可以突然間就唔愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以教吓我 我都想就咁放低你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc8cddd4055214be9694032ed823ec747a0b1eb","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"肥仔話佢地都好多炒大獲㗎 但慢慢溝通磨合互相遷就就可以解決問題啦<br />\n佢地下年結婚啦 我以為我同你都得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aced3c3a2ee82deb638a82317d11d2af6f2e0af","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4881f7131761e24a16a64a0897a1fa7d40e2072","tid":1561000,"uid":75013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"我都好想嫁比你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解你唔肯同返我一齊 點解唔可以一齊渡過呢個冷淡期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"講到底 可能都係因為唔愛了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e2e31fe59b2dd4d4b283ab730c9e0264979ae8","tid":1561000,"uid":151451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c076261f21d908b42945bff0fb0ed7e793f467d","tid":1561000,"uid":31215,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"冇架喇<br />\n向前望<br />\n就好似你飲開凍奶茶，未飲過其他野，以為世界得凍奶茶，忽然間冇得飲梗係失落<br />\n到你遇上凍檸茶，雖然味道唔同，但都好飲，你有時會諗返凍奶茶嘅味，但凍檸茶都夠你快樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"我淨係想